  "description": "Product workflow for pi.dev: Shape Up + Interface + Tech Planning + Critique + Gate. Includes 16 product skills: workflow, short-cycle, opportunity-mapping, job-to-be-done, evolutionary, ads, business-models, health, marketplace-playbook, open-source, pricing, promotions, trust-building, multi-method-market-analysis, scope-executor, testing-ai-code. Integrates with pi-subagents (nicobailon), pi-goal (capyup), plannotator (backnotprop), autoresearch (davebcn87), ask-user-question (juicesharp), intercom (nicobailon), supervisor (tintinweb), and pi-agent-codebase-workflows (PriNova).",
